        "text": "Hello everyone! :wave: My name is Salmen and I am developer and open-source contributor based in London.\n\nI'm currently working at <https:\/\/www.ag-grid.com\/|AG Grid> and I have a side-hustle project called <https:\/\/nlux.ai|NLUX>: A React \/ JS library to create AI chatbots.\n\nI am fascinated by LLM-powered chatbots and I spend a lot of time thinking how AI will impact software development and user-interfaces.\n\n*If anyone in the group is building AI chatbots, websites or web apps that use conversational interfaces, <https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/hichri\/|I would like to connect> and chat!* :handshake: :slightly_smiling_face:  :speech_balloon:\n\nAnecdote: This is what I get on Runway ML and I use the prompt:\n\"_If a React JS developer were to design a pair of Nike shoes, how would it look like?_\" :shushing_face: :atom_symbol:",
